6 DECOMPOSITION FOR MULTIPLE  ADVERSARIES :
6-1:ADVERSARIES The MILP developed in the previous section handles only one follower .
6-2:Since our security scenario contains multiple follower (robber) types, we change the response function for the follower from a pure strategy into a weighted combination over various pure follower strategies where the weights are probabilities of occurrence of each of the follower types .
6-3:5.1 Decomposed MIQP To admit multiple adversaries in our framework, we modify the notation defined in the previous section to reason about multiple follower types .
